summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 231W, Page 24 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone Lot 10, Engstrom's Addition to the City of Seattle located at 8515 12th Ave. N.W. from RS 5000 to RM 800, and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (C.F. 287397, Petition of Kenneth P. Gronvold).
